source: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_SEQ_00<tab>Halfsix seems to be giggling to himself.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_SEQ_00<tab>Halfsix a l'air de mijoter une mauvaise blague.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_SEQ_01<tab>Halfsix has seemingly crafted devices able to interrupt Illuminati communications. Now, he wishes you to plant these contraptions around the Makers' Quarter, so as to vex the mortal enemies of Idyllshire. Make your way to the Dravanian hinterlands, and set up the three jamming devices now.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_SEQ_01<tab>Halfsix souhaite gêner les Gobelins de la Main indigo avec ses “<var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8B300302 /var>” faits maison. Placez les trois appareils aux <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E9B720302 /var> qu'il vous a indiqués.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_SEQ_02<tab>You plant all three jamming devices in a crescent pattern around the Arkhitekton. Report back to Halfsix, and tell him the great “joke” you two have played on Illuminati.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez mis en place les <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8B300302 /var>. Retournez voir Halfsix.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_SEQ_03<tab>Upon hearing that the deed is done, Halfsix must stifle his own laughter when imagining exactly how frustrating it will be for the Illuminati to lose their ability to communicate. Though he does not thank you in so many words, you sense you have won the goblin's trust.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_SEQ_03<tab>Halfsix est ravi à l'idée que des Gobelins de la Main indigo vont sans doute se faire piéger par ses appareils.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_TODO_00<tab>Plant jamming devices throughout the Makers' Quarter.

TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_HALFSIX_000_000<tab>Pshkohhh... Is uplander looking to aid Idyllshire? Then uplander has come to right gobbie! Halfsix has tricksy plan, will drive Illuminati out of their braincases!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_HALFSIX_000_000<tab>Pshhh... Pshhh... L<var 08 E905 ((a)) ((e)) /var> gentil<var 08 E905 ((le)) (()) /var> aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> cherche du travail<var 1D /var>? Halfsix a un travail à proposer<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_HALFSIX_000_001<tab>Psssheehee! Here, take these inventions of Halfsix, name of signalclogger. If uplander puts them up in Makers' Quarter, they will stop all Illuminati airtalking!
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_HALFSIX_000_001<tab>Voilà des <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8B300302 /var> faits par Halfsix<var 1D /var>! Halfsix veut embêter la Main indigo avec<var 1D /var>! La Main indigo pourra plus entendre ses communications près de ces appareils... Mais il faut les disposer quelque part, d'abord<var 1D /var>! L<var 08 E905 ((a)) ((e)) /var> gentil<var 08 E905 ((le)) (()) /var> aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> voudrait bien le faire pour Halfsix<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_HALFSIX_000_010<tab>Psssheehee! Can uplander imagine Illuminati airtalking while signalclogger is on? “Hello? Hello? Can you hear me?”
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_HALFSIX_000_010<tab>Halfsix veut embêter la Main indigo avec des <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8B300302 /var> faits maison<var 1D /var>! La Main indigo pourra plus entendre ses communications près de ces appareils... Mais il faut les disposer quelque part, d'abord<var 1D /var>! L<var 08 E905 ((a)) ((e)) /var> gentil<var 08 E905 ((le)) (()) /var> aventuri<var 08 E905 ((ère)) ((er)) /var> voudrait bien le faire pour Halfsix<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_HALFSIX_000_030<tab>Pshkohhh... Now Illuminati cannot airtalk over linkpearl, must walk all the way from one end of Makers' Quarter all the way to the other to make tongueflaps! Halfsix and uplander have played very good trick, no?
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ810_01940_HALFSIX_000_030<tab>Psssh, psshhh... Halfsix aime embêter la Main indigo avec de vilaines farces<var 1D /var>! Bien fait pour leur tronche<var 1D /var>!
